        University Technician in Computer Science
      </h2>
      <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl md:text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-semibold bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-600 to-purple-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
        Full Stack Developer
      </h3>
    </div>

    <!-- DescripciÃ³n profesional -->
    <div class="max-w-2xl">
      <p class="text-base sm:text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
